-- Irish Mortgages in Arrears to Exceed 10%, Business Post Says
-- B y   F i n b a r r   F l y n n
-- 2012-05-20T08:09:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-20/irish-mortgages-in-arrears-to-exceed-10-business-post-says.html
Irish home loans in arrears for more
than 90 days may have risen to 10.5 percent in the first quarter
from 9.2 percent at the end of last year, the  Sunday Business
Post  reported, citing “informed sources.”  The Irish central bank is scheduled to release quarterly
data this week, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporters on this story:
